<plot>"Story Time" is a compilation of video stories that only young women could tell. Subjects addressed in these films include the importance of choosing one's own personal style, a young Iranian woman questioning her choice to wear the hijab in the US, the effect of media consolidation on youth, and a novel and humorous look at stereotypes in modern society.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?516858</url></doc>
